Ingredients
Eggplant

Sauce:
Canned tomatoes
Onion
Salt
Sugar
Italian herbs
Basil leaves

Cheese:
Mozzarella cheese (fresh)
Parmesan cheese




Method
Eggplant:

Cut eggplant into slices, sprinkle salt and leave it for 15-20 minutes
Wash eggplant to remove salt, and pat it dry
Grill eggplant slices on pan
Tomato sauce:

Sauté onions and garlic till well cooked
Add canned tomatoes
Add salt, sugar, herbs
Add basil leaves
Cheese:

Grate the cheeses
Assemble:

In a dish, spread sauce at the bottom
Add layer of eggplant
Add cheese
Add sauce
Add layer of eggplant
Add cheese
Add sauce
Add layer of eggplant
Add sauce
Add cheese
Oven:

Preheat oven to 210 C
Cook the dish in the oven for 20-30 min or until cheese has melted and become brown





